Looking south, 1936 (&lt;i&gt;USC Digital Archives&lt;/i&gt;).  Skinny building to the east of Marcella is the Winton Apts at 219 S Flower; bottom left is 208 S Figueroa (seen below, &lt;i&gt;Cal State Library, William Reagh&lt;/i&gt;).  The big building at top is the Stanley, southeast corner Second and Flower.
